subject: Dear ,
body:
Dear ,
It’s shocking that after the new year I haven’t heard from you.. I never believe that whole deal will suddenly end this way without any notice from your end.  I can’t comprehend reason behind your actions.
Shirley.

subject: Re:   Dear ,
body:
Dear Shirley,

I apologize for the delay in my response. The new year has been quite busy and I've had a lot on my plate. I assure you that it was not my intention to end our deal abruptly or without notice. 

Could you please remind me of the details of our agreement? I want to make sure we're on the same page moving forward.

Best wishes,
Victor
